Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, {\i1}this{\i0} classic scene. It's just like they always say:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If "sorry" was enough, then we wouldn't need the police, would we?{until iranain ja nai}
