Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have cooperated with the police in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no doubt that Talisman has gotten caught up in some sort of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped us because you felt you couldn't just ignore that, right?
