Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spooky Boogie, the anarchist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Under no circumstances will I ever act as your agent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news for your friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she was just someone who used to be in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know who she is, really.
