Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Talisman Saloon is packed with guests, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is another busy day for the ghost of Hayama Kimihiko, as he dispenses advice without a care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only is he not running or hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he's even been talking about what happened in Club Exoset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point, just what is his game here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Was his goal to make it look like Hayama Kimihiko was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no way he'd leave\N Hayama's bank account untouched
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and his apartment empty for two months, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if his goal really was simply to gain control of Hayama's Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see someone who commits crimes for kicks doing that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would someone like that kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gino, don't try to understand the minds of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be taken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that warning directed at me or yourself, Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this guy's just doing it for kicks, he's no fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He anticipated that he'd fall under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he could have cracked the Holo-Cosplay in the hall unless he'd prepared beforehand.{until soudan da}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If he thinks he can play us like fools, we'll have to teach him a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Karanomori, trace Talisman's access routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out who he is and capture him this time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too worked up, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's clearly very confident in his ability to hide his tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's still hanging around the social networks as if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's the point in us sitting around doing nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be another way to get a lead on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more thing that I want to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still going to trace his access routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get stuff like Avatars and virtual worlds.{until dekin / scene change}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean after all, it's our bodies that actually breathe, sweat, and eat, right?{gotta have that oxford comma}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaoka, I think people like you are an endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't using the net just like using knives for cooking or using paper to write things down?{until desu ka ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not intrisically good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just there, so we accept it and use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at explaining things, aren't you? Like a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of Rousseau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You mean the philosopher?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And his work "A Discourse on Inequality."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, please. I'll look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all stored right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say there are two hunters in a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Should they hunt for rabbits separately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Should they work together and go after bigger prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you think is the better option?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The latter, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a basic rule of game theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You work together to catch bigger prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Humans are social by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Languages, letters, currencies, telephones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All the communication tools that exist in the world are there in order to strengthen social nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the net has the same effect, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I think it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... That sounds kinda interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall I give you a bit of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wouldn't be a bad idea to get one of the Public Safety Bureau's rising stars in my debt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... That sounds kinda interesting. {intentionally repeated}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall I give you a bit of assistance? {this too}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If "sorry" was enough, then we wouldn't need the police, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never should have cooperated with the police in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never should have cooperated with the police in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her choice of words is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, she used "Public Safety Bureau". Now, "police."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think it's just a coincidence?
